Detailed Description

This Structure defines the configuration for running TESOC test. These parameters are used for configuring domainType and slice configuration.

Field Documentation

uint32_t tesocTestCfg::completionIntrEnable

Flag to enable TESOC test completion interrupt

uint32_t tesocTestCfg::domainLabel

Domain label for running TESOC test on. Refer enum #tesocDomainLabel_t for details

uint32_t tesocTestCfg::sliceTestBlock[TESOC_NUM_SLICE_BLOCKS]

Array containing slice numbers on which test is run

uint32_t tesocTestCfg::testId

Test ID for running TESOC test. Refer enum #tesocTestId_t for details
